entries.title_d: Destroy Ay'Nat pirates throughout the Naboo System
entries.title: Naboo System: Duty: Hunt down Ay'Nat Pirate Legion
entries.taunt_5: Time to add another RSF puppet on my kill list!
entries.taunt_4: The Ay'Nat Legion leave no survivors!
entries.taunt_3: You are a fool to engage the Ay'Nat Legion!
entries.taunt_2: Royal Security Force? More like Royally Slow Fools!
entries.taunt_1: I guess not all RSF is on our payroll. No matter, you won't be on anyones payroll after this!
entries.targets_detected: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Vessels fitting hunted ship profile on attack vector, weapon systems armed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.targets_behind: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Be aware, vessels trying to target this ship with their weapon systems. Attack originating direction 180 degrees. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: Areas of Ay'Nat activity throughout the Naboo System
entries.quest_destroy_d: Proceed to this point and engage Ay'Nat craft
entries.level_increase: Sensors through out the system show increased Ay'Nat Pirate activity in response to our attacks.
entries.level_boss_dead: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 That one has been a dread ever since he came to this sector, great work pilot! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.level_boss: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Ay'Nat Legion have sent one of their best pilots to take care of you, be careful! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The next area of known Ay'Nat Legion activity has been uploaded to your nav computer, proceed when ready. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: Your pilot helmet will look good on my trophy rack RSF fool!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: Maybe I should fly using just one hand, to give you a chance?
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: Too bad you ran in to me so early in your career, as I mark it's end!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_1: Foolish RSF puppet, you should have run while you had the chance!
entries.complete: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Fantastic job pilot! We struck a blow to the Ay'Nat Legion that will take them a long time to recover from. Head back to base when ready. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.boss_detected: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Ay'Nat Warlord on attack vector, weapon systems armed. \#pcontrast3 >
